{"tid":2212774,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"許章潤再發公開信撐耿瀟男夫婦 籲法學家勿助紂為虐","createTime":"2020-09-22T05:06:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-22T05:14:08.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a22e4dd7404ad8c79e81fd98866a178e96ed7e23","tid":2212774,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T05:06:03.000Z","msg":"遭清華大學開除的中國法家許章潤日前再於社交媒體發文，聲援其好友、上月被北京警方刑事拘留的中國企業家耿瀟男和她的丈夫。許斥中國存在多少「口袋罪」，「想治你，就把你裝進去」。呼籲中國刑法學家們深刻反省立惡法的罪過，不要繼續助紂為虐。所謂「口袋罪」，是指界定不清，以至難以界定有罪與否的罪名<br />\n<br />\n獨立出版人，為一大批公職人士奔走的耿瀟男早前被以「非法經營罪」抓捕後，許章潤教授9月10日發出「就女子羈獄致暴政書」，奉勸當局還耿瀟男夫婦自由和還這個世界公道：「別作惡，放下屠刀」。9月17日，許章潤再發出「致疑刑法學家」公開信，呼籲刑法學家不要出賣自己，知錯就改。<br />\n<br />\n許章潤指出，1979年〈刑法〉曾規定，「投機倒把」與「流氓」兩罪，多年來成為「拿捏隨心」，不知冤枉了多少人，成為所謂的「口袋罪」，「想治你，就把你裝進去」，後來才得以修訂，算是知錯就改。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200922/H2WT6VFLGFDHVIQGN4CSET6J3E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200922%2FH2WT6VFLGFDHVIQGN4CSET6J3E%2F&d=UI3sabJMorhQDzR%2BXF3zEaDCEJE6krTJKQ6%2BfiBCJRk%3D&h=25e656ee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200922%2FH2WT6VFLGFDHVIQGN4CSET6J3E%2F&h=e56909f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200922/H2WT6VFLGFDHVIQGN4CSET6J3E/</a>"},{"pid":"3fc781a987eaabae6cfa42909b3370f4d0afff25","tid":2212774,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T05:12:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cae16448aa9e6946201fa2fb2d8e6184e32b734f","tid":2212774,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3fc781a987eaabae6cfa42909b3370f4d0afff25","tid":2212774,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T05:12:3